<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/higher-education-statistical-agency> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "HESA collect, process and publish data about higher education in the UK, supporting and enhancing the competitive strength of the sector. HESA works with the Department for Business, Innovation & Skills ."@en .
